# Low-token session

- Default **short** answers; elaborate only when asked or ambiguity would cost extra turns.
- Do **not** restate unchanged constraints each reply.
- Prefer bullets over paragraphs; cite paths instead of pasting big excerpts.
- Omit filler praise and redundant recaps unless the task requires proofreading tone.
